title: Firemen Rescue Suspects in Overturned Car
description: A dramatic scene shows firemen rescuing men from an overturned car. One man is visibly distressed, being helped by two others. The bottom image contains a news slip detailing the event, mentioning that the individuals were trapped in the vehicle and freed by firemen. The event occurred in San Francisco, and the photo is credited to Jack Gorman.
